<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thanks for Applying!</h1>

    <p>
    <%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.first_name %>, your scholarship application has been recieved, you should hear from us within the next two days. Below is a confirmation of your application.
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>First name:</strong>
    <%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.first_name %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Last name:</strong>
    <%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.last_name %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Email:</strong>
    <%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.email %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Phone:</strong>
    <%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.phone %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Age:</strong>
    <%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.age %>
    </p>
    <p>
    <strong>Write a couple of paragraphs about a time you faced a challenge in life and overcame it:</strong>
    <%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.reason %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Why should we choose you to be a student in this program?</strong>
    <%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.career %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Relevant links:</strong>
    <%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.links %>
    </p>

    <p>
    <strong>Portfolio:</strong>
    <a href="<%= @women_in_tech_scholarship.portfolio %>" target="_blank">Click here to download</a>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
